  "_pricing_note": "SELL credits = credit_catalog.video_credits_for_usd(official_usd, cogs_usd, seconds, markup=VIDEO_SELL_MARKUP default 1.10) → max(official*markup, 2*cogs) per-second * seconds / credit_usd_value, round-up-to-5. Tool ops price off op-chain MAX. credit_usd_value = 0.002 (shared with image). badge == charge."
